Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 画这个漫画的山内是什么样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是个男高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些段子只有男高中生能想出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说 说不定就是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Comment: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
