Comment: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//PS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 从画风上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是男子小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹啊 当我是傻瓜么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 从刚才开始就一直在抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责山内的编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这货不是山内吗！
