Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.98,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}{\bord3\3c&HF48C16&\pos(858,673)\fad(600,700)\blur10}男子高中生与配音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是中学生么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五和中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五和中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹得真起劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她们配上台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 邪门歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不让你活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 店内请保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了你付钱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你点干鲍鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你跟我去事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年时光过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了 你们出狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 做年糕来庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去把年糕翻一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 年糕跑到眼睛里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被驱逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会白死 死也要找你垫背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 世界被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说那边三个人从刚才就一直盯着咱们  你们不觉得恶心么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对是看上我们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 坏了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说自己还一脸残念吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:05.96,TITLE2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\bord2\3c&H896827&\pos(1275,370)\blur0.5}装成配音演员来配个音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:05.96,TITLE2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\bord2\3c&H896827&\pos(58,331)\blur0.5}超现实主义工种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子高中生的日常  由以上赞助商提供
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咣当一下播出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:10.92,TITLE2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\bord2\3c&H896827&\pos(1275,370)\blur0.5}今天依然加量不加价
