Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:10.69,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE151EF&}{\bord3\blur5}就在你心里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子高中生很异常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不对  太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪里不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！曲子和动作一点都不协调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩儿这种女子乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光会被男生们看不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能乘着这女高中生热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带动拖把和扫把一周里疯狂卖掉一年的量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（注：说的是KON!大卖导致主角使用的乐器被哄抢一空的事情）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更产生不了走出国门前往伦敦的经济效果啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（注：KON！舞台在伦敦）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  能去伦敦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们本来就不是那种设定的动画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  给我打气精神练习
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:21:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子高中生很异常嗷嗷嗷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.72,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}{\bord3\3c&H2522B2&\pos(1083,650)\fad(600,700)\blur9}怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁的俊之君虽然给了我们零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.92,0:22:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都是过期了的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种你别挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我立正啊  立正
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  站稳了别动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别挡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生岛  困住他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  老老实实地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子该适可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股它…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这伪君子有什么资格瞧不起我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在该知道自己到底有多卑琐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连活着都嫌寒碜了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪下吧  给我跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见我们说话没你这沙门氏菌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊之君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伤的事  事到如今也别太在意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都那么多年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很会开玩笑嘛  羽原
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然赔钱啥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太次了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:59.73,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}{\bord1\3c&HF48C16&\pos(615,456)\fad(300,0)\blur9}「男子高中生与圣诞夜」及其他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  圣诞节…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这季节变换太无常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:04.70,TITLE2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\bord2\3c&H896827&\pos(1275,353)\blur0.5}于是乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:04.70,TITLE2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\bord2\3c&H896827&\pos(58,331)\blur0.5}季节终于赶上进度了
